2670 // Add a VPActiveLaneMaskPHIRecipe and related recipes to \p Plan and replace
2671 // the loop terminator with a branch-on-cond recipe with the negated
2672 // active-lane-mask as operand. Note that this turns the loop into an
2673 // uncountable one. Only the existing terminator is replaced, all other existing
2674 // recipes/users remain unchanged, except for poison-generating flags being
2675 // dropped from the canonical IV increment. Return the created
2676 // VPActiveLaneMaskPHIRecipe.
2677 //
2678 // The function uses the following definitions:
2679 //
2680 //  %TripCount = DataWithControlFlowWithoutRuntimeCheck ?
2681 //    calculate-trip-count-minus-VF (original TC) : original TC
2682 //  %IncrementValue = DataWithControlFlowWithoutRuntimeCheck ?
2683 //     CanonicalIVPhi : CanonicalIVIncrement
2684 //  %StartV is the canonical induction start value.
